{"tid":1771991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族陣綫 海外支援計劃 重新啟動！","createTime":"2019-12-06T09:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T09:56:51.000Z","uid":56428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6edb48af6a537c459fb8b77bbf953652c35f6f","tid":1771991,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:06:03.000Z","msg":"［海外支援計劃 重新啟動！］￼￼<br />\n<br />\n早前本組織與自由台灣黨合作，推動海外支援計劃，除了希望為反送中抗爭提供支援之外，更希望為流亡海外的抗爭者提供進一步支援。<br />\n然而計劃開展不足半天，用作籌款的PayPal戶口已被凍結，所籌得捐款無法提取，因此近月來所有個案的撥款只能由本組織代墊。<br />\n為確保計劃有足夠資金能夠繼續進行，本組織未來將會收取Bitcoin捐款，以下為簡單教學，希望各位能夠慷慨解囊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/78792879_2516444201930608_8625487047081066496_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_ohc=zzVFNuwmkxgAQn1hPhBT47WeYoDjOwZcNJd2d6ke-fr2sV4jmfM10LJCw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=b178781bbc4ed6f9ef893f90529e8564&amp;oe=5E75869E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F78792879_2516444201930608_8625487047081066496_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_ohc%3DzzVFNuwmkxgAQn1hPhBT47WeYoDjOwZcNJd2d6ke-fr2sV4jmfM10LJCw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3Db178781bbc4ed6f9ef893f90529e8564%26oe%3D5E75869E&h=fbb2a420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/78450113_2516444238597271_2025578410121625600_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_ohc=hGrFRamr4Q8AQmM0Hmm4XdHOt0EPY4F3FMnsVi8CLCcw--KBzWwkMGlXw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=3b1b3ddeb0c00d94a680852a885089a9&amp;oe=5E78B323\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F78450113_2516444238597271_2025578410121625600_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_ohc%3DhGrFRamr4Q8AQmM0Hmm4XdHOt0EPY4F3FMnsVi8CLCcw--KBzWwkMGlXw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D3b1b3ddeb0c00d94a680852a885089a9%26oe%3D5E78B323&h=7d972275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/78295748_2516444285263933_74